data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
Two rules: - Each Manual must be in a folder having the same system name AS the name in launchbox. ex: F:\CheadCodes\Sega Megadrive\ && in LaunchBox the system is named Sega Megadrive => Enter F:\CheadCodes\ - To select the manuals, they must have a name beginning by the Name of the game + "-" +(optionnal) something ex: For Sonic, Cheadcode archive must begin by 'Sonic-'
Note: As much archive as you want.
